905838-33-5|language=en|last=Jürgen Domes|title=Socialism in the Chinese Countryside: Rural Societal Policies in the People's Republic of China, 1949-1979|quote=Even conservative sources estimate that there were no less than 5 million victims of the land reform movement.}}</ref><ref name="voa">{{cite web|title=1949之后：土改何以要杀人？|url=http://www.voachinese.com/content/a-21-c2007-10-26-voa64-62992217/1038774.html|author=李肃|date=2007-12-02|publisher=[[美国之音|美国之音]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140502082735/http://www.voachinese.com/content/a-21-c2007-10-26-voa64-62992217/1038774.html|archive-date=2014-05-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
